ere%20previously%20able%20to%20git-clone%20from%20an%20unpublished%20repo%20via%20the%20projection%20path%2C%20they%20can%20no%20longer%20do%20so.%0A%0AHow%20can%20I%20resolve%20this%3F%20If%20you%20propose%20a%20fix%2C%20please%20make%20it%20concise.&repo=adamblumoff%2Fscope-vcs&pr=86&platform=github\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://greptile-static-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/badges/FixInCodexDark.svg?v=6\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://greptile-static-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/badges/FixInCodex.svg?v=6\"><img alt=\"Fix in Codex\" src=\"https://greptile-static-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/badges/FixInCodex.svg?v=6\"></picture></a>",
