s%20record%20for%20an%20owner%2C%20confirm%20the%20intent%20is%20to%20serve%20public%20content%20to%20them%20rather%20than%20a%20panic%2Ferror.%20Can%20%60can_read_private_files%60%20ever%20be%20%60false%60%20for%20an%20%60Owner%60%20actor%2C%20and%20is%20serving%20them%20the%20public%20projection%20the%20intended%20fallback%3F%0A%0AHow%20can%20I%20resolve%20this%3F%20If%20you%20propose%20a%20fix%2C%20please%20make%20it%20concise.&repo=adamblumoff%2Fscope-vcs&pr=86&platform=github\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://greptile-static-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/badges/FixInCodexDark.svg?v=6\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://greptile-static-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/badges/FixInCodex.svg?v=6\"><img alt=\"Fix in Codex\" src=\"https://greptile-static-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/badges/FixInCodex.svg?v=6\"></picture></a>",
